---
title: Swedish Pork Meatballs & Creamy Bacon Sauce with Garlicky Greens & Cheesy Mash
description: We've given our go-to meatballs a Swedish-inspired twist by topping them with a creamy sauce that's so good, everyone will be asking you how you made it. Serve with a Parmesan-laced mash and almond-adorned garlicky greens for the ultimate crowd-pleaser!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/668738be98a5211d32d1d06c-11714d8a.jpeg
